description:
This is a 19 minute workout called 'Guided Meditation For Anxiety | SURRENDER SESSION | Letting Go' from the channel The Anxiety Guy.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation and Rest/Breathing exercises.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Let me be your guide to true and lasting anxiety recovery starting today, click here: https://dennissimsek.com/anxiety-programs/

The Benefits of this Guided Meditation for Anxiety: Learning to Let Go

In today's fast-paced world, many people struggle with anxiety and its accompanying challenges. One powerful tool that has gained popularity in recent years is guided meditations for anxiety. By incorporating this surrender specific guided meditation for anxiety into your routine, you will learn to let go of anxiety and experience a multitude of benefits for your mental and emotional well-being such as:

1. Cultivating Relaxation Response:
This guided meditation for anxiety will activate the body's relaxation response, which counteracts the stress response triggered by anxiety. Through soothing and calming instructions, guided meditation prompts deep relaxation, slowing down your heart rate, reducing blood pressure, and easing muscle tension.
